messages.messageBody:
"Also, she's an introvert, hates transitions and new places etc."

There are many of those at the conference.:)
A few of them spend most of their time up in their rooms, but more
often than not, they find a few friends and some funshops to attend.

Wait until Kelly gets the funshop listings up and read her some of
those. Promise her she can stay up in the room with food and video
games (or books or??) and it would mean a LOT to both of you if she'd go.

Is there anything you could tempt her with in Albuquerque that you
don't have in your town?

Ren
learninginfreedom.com
